<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-81-0814 </DOCNO><TEXT>In order to study the magnetization curves of hard magnetic materialsas a function of their microstructure, the effect of a misalignment ofthe grain in a fine particle magnet NdFeB is investigated theoreticallytaking into account the higher order anisotropy constant (K). The externalhysteresis loops for K'/sub 1/ = -0.3 and K'/sub 2/ = 1 are plotted forthe texture parameters n = 0 and n = 5.</TEXT></DOC>